Use a CSV File as a Data Source

Upload large amounts of CSV file data into your definition with the Data Cloud runtime. Add the CSV file in a data source node and configure the fields to use in the definition. After a definition is run, download any failed records in Monitor Workflow Services.

NOTE This feature is not generally available and is being piloted with certain Customers subject to additional terms and conditions. It is not part of your purchased Services. This feature is subject to change, may be discontinued with no notice at any time in Salesforce’s sole discretion, and Salesforce may never make this feature generally available.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Data Processing Engine is enabled.
